  "body": "\r\nAutopath server-side lookups are not being performed when issuing dns queries from pods in the cluster.\r\n\r\nI tested with the following configuration...\r\n\r\n```\r\n    .:53 {\r\n      health\r\n      errors\r\n      log\r\n      autopath cluster.local @kubernetes\r\n      kubernetes cluster.local {\r\n        pods verified\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n```\r\n\r\nI see the following warning in the logs ...\r\n```\r\n2017/09/06 17:48:53 [WARNING] No search path available for autopath\r\n```\r\n.. suggesting that autopath middleware is not able to get the kubernetes search path.",
